    <abstract>
      <t>RFC1122 defines nodes TCP stack behavior for ICMPv4 error messages,
   but does not for ICMPv6.  This document defines ICMPv6 message
   classification and node's TCP stack behavior for ICMPv6.</t>
    </abstract>
